======================================================================

                         find_int_digits

             Use this function if you want to find
           the number of digits of an integer number.

    For example:
        Given integer number: 0x00139AFE (1284862),
        the function will find out how many digits in the
        number. The function will return 7, means 7 digits.

----------------------------------------------------------------------

 DIRECTORY INFORMATION

     doc: Contains documentations about the function.
 example: Some basic tutorials on how to use this function.
     src: Contains source code.
    test: For testing purpose, to ensure the function has no error.

